channel.description:
[center][b][size=3]Get your free web client today![/size][/b][/center] [center][b]I promise I will never rip you off, and if there's something that you don't like, tell me or get a MoparScape staff to ban me.[/b] ;)[/center]
[center]Try my test web client at [url=http://x-isle.hostei.com/play.php]http://x-isle.hostei.com/play.php[/url][/center] [center]Firefox works better with web clients![/center]
[center]Hello MoparScape! I'm Sway, and I'm here to tell you that I am willing to make web clients for anyone no matter what. All you have to do is email me at [email]tom.vanyo@gmail.com[/email] or add my msn at [email]tom_hugo@hotmail.com[/email][/center]
[b]Now there are a few things you have to follow.[/b]
[u]First:[/u] Make an account at [url=http://000webhost.com]000webhost.com[/url]. Don't worry, its free and easy!
[u]Second:[/u] Email/Message me your WinRAR/WinZip/7-Zip/G-Zip/ 'ed client with your user-name and password for your site and the site name. Also with that, you need to tell me the name you wish to sign the jar file.
[u]Third:[/u] Keep in touch with me until I say the web client is done!
[center]That's it! I hope you love you web client![/center] [center]NOTE: Web clients are only for 317 - 474 clients[/center]
Dear MoparScape Moderator, If there are [i]any[/i] reports of me cheating people, please ban me.
Sincerely, Sway :)
